quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  27,1,"Twa, Sin. Etso ni tsinyaali tsia Ikurani, nende eshitabu shinoosinjia."
  27,2,"Obulunjifu nende omwikhoyoro khubasuubili."
  27,3,"Balia balumililanga okhulaama (iswala) nende okhurusia eshihanwa (izaaka), nabo bali nobusuubili muno bwo mwikulu."
  27,4,"Toto balia balasuubilanga mwikulu tawe, khwabaronela ebikhole biabu, mana bayiyayiyanga."
  27,5,"Abo nibo baliba nende eshinyasio eshibii, nabo mwikulu nibo balinyoola okhusikha muno."
  27,6,"Ne toto ewe wechesibungwa Ikurani okhurula khu Wamachesi, Omumanyi muno."
  27,7,"(Itsulila) olwa Musa yaboolela Abandu beyinzu yiyie mbu: “Toto esie endutsi omulilo. Bulano buri nditsa okhubarerera amacheni kali khumulilo oko, nohomba nditsa okhubarerera eshichenga shiakhanga mwakhaba murio mwanyoola okhwora (omulilo).""
  27,8,"Kho, olwa yakuulakhwo, yalangwa mbu: “Ali netsikhabi owuli mumulilo kuno nende ulia uli mundulo mwakwo, ne Nyasaye noomutswenufu, Omulesi webiloonje bioosi."
  27,9,"Ewe Musa, toto esie nesie Nyasaye owa Amaani, Owamachesi muno.""
  27,10,"Ne sukuna indabushi yiyio.” Olwa yayilola nimoolanga shinga inzokha, yakalukhana inyuma niyelukha, ne shiyalinda tawe. Nyasaye namuboolela: “Ewe Musa, olaria tawe, toto esie, Abarumwa shibabetsanga noburi imbeli wanje tawe."
  27,11,"Halali ulia wakhola obubii, mana nakalukhania obulayi habundu wobubii, toto esie endi Omunji wobulesheli, Omunji wetsimbabaasi."
  27,12,"Ne injisia omukhono kukwo mumufuko kwao, kularulamwo nikuli omulafu tswe bulali khububii tawe. Ni ndala khubimanyisio tisa bitsie khu Firauni nende Abandu bebe. Toto abo bali abandu abakholi ba tsimbi.”"
  27,13,"Mana olwa ebimanyisio biefu biaboolela nibilolekhanga, baboola mbu: “Buno ni obulosi obwahabulafu.”"